&lt;p&gt;Maybe it is related to log4j shutdown hooks (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-2176&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-2176&lt;/a&gt;) so I tried to disable the hook in my src/test/resources/log4j2.xml.&lt;/p&gt;

